This is the read me file for GeneTorrent

Directory Contents

src                 GeneTorrent src directory
libtorrent          libtorrent src directory
README              This file
LICENSE             GeneTorrent and other license information
GeneTorrent.spec    File required to construct a GeneTorrent RPM
scripts             Utility Scripts-part of GeneTorrent not the build process
init.d              config files and init scripts
boost               contains a script to build the required boost libraries
                    (if necessary)
openssl             contains a script to build the required openssl
                    (if necessary)

Build Requirements:

This package has been tested with the following minimum library versions:

xerces-c 2.7.0
xqilla 2.0.0
libcurl 7.15.5
openssl 1.0.1a
boost 1.48.0

If using the source release of GeneTorrent, Boost 1.48 must be built without
icu support.

Build Options:

To enable verbose logging, configure with --enable-logging=verbose

To create a debug build, configure with --enable-debug --enable-logging=verbose
